00:00:54.210 --> 00:00:58.600 align:middle line:84%
>> About 11 years ago, I came
and visited this place, omega,

00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:00.030 align:middle line:90%
these beautiful surroundings.

00:01:00.030 --> 00:01:03.450 align:middle line:84%
I was a very unhappy
lawyer at the time,

00:01:03.450 --> 00:01:07.480 align:middle line:84%
and I took a yoga
class at the time.

00:01:07.480 --> 00:01:09.120 align:middle line:84%
And there was a
woman across the room

00:01:09.120 --> 00:01:12.180 align:middle line:84%
just exuding a beautiful,
great, radiant spirit

00:01:12.180 --> 00:01:14.460 align:middle line:90%
with a big smile on her face.

00:01:14.460 --> 00:01:16.320 align:middle line:84%
And I found myself
wanting to talk to her

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:18.030 align:middle line:90%
and get to know her.

00:01:18.030 --> 00:01:21.360 align:middle line:90%
And that woman became my wife.

00:01:21.360 --> 00:01:26.690 align:middle line:84%
That woman became a great source
of incredible love in my life.

00:01:26.690 --> 00:01:32.090 align:middle line:84%
I was here and distraught and
upset with my life, and she--

00:01:32.090 --> 00:01:35.420 align:middle line:84%
she was someone who said,
surrender to the best in you.

00:01:35.420 --> 00:01:37.240 align:middle line:90%
Do whatever you want to do.

00:01:37.240 --> 00:01:38.040 align:middle line:90%
I love you.

00:01:38.040 --> 00:01:40.260 align:middle line:84%
I'll live in a
thatched hut with you.

00:01:40.260 --> 00:01:41.250 align:middle line:90%
Leave the law.

00:01:41.250 --> 00:01:43.430 align:middle line:10%
I don't care about how
much money you were making.

00:01:43.430 --> 00:01:45.240 align:middle line:84%
Do something, and
follow your heart.

00:01:45.240 --> 00:01:47.190 align:middle line:90%
Go with what's in you.

00:01:47.190 --> 00:01:50.790 align:middle line:84%
So we wind up getting
married, and we

00:01:50.790 --> 00:01:53.970 align:middle line:84%
have a beautiful five-year-old
son who's here with us

00:01:53.970 --> 00:01:56.670 align:middle line:90%
this weekend.

00:01:56.670 --> 00:02:00.180 align:middle line:84%
In the last 11 years, I've
seen the total transformation

00:02:00.180 --> 00:02:02.040 align:middle line:90%
in my life.

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:03.200 align:middle line:90%
I left the law.

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:06.150 align:middle line:84%
I totally retired
from being a lawyer,

00:02:06.150 --> 00:02:08.820 align:middle line:84%
because I wanted a whole
different consciousness.

00:02:08.820 --> 00:02:10.350 align:middle line:84%
This joke in this
shirt, "Trust me--

00:02:10.350 --> 00:02:12.960 align:middle line:84%
I'm a lawyer," the
lawyer being the shark,

00:02:12.960 --> 00:02:16.950 align:middle line:84%
well, he's the one that society
has to protect, to defend,

00:02:16.950 --> 00:02:18.450 align:middle line:90%
to go after.

00:02:18.450 --> 00:02:24.630 align:middle line:84%
