00:14:41.140 --> 00:14:45.200 align:middle line:84%
in the wilderness above the
cloud line, above the tree--

00:14:45.200 --> 00:14:47.200 align:middle line:84%
well, there were some
trees up there, but mostly

00:14:47.200 --> 00:14:52.090 align:middle line:84%
above the tree line, and really
sat and watched the world.

00:14:52.090 --> 00:14:54.230 align:middle line:84%
And not only the
period of isolation,

00:14:54.230 --> 00:14:57.760 align:middle line:84%
but the period of
removal from this culture

00:14:57.760 --> 00:15:01.090 align:middle line:84%
that I was born and raised
in, like the rest of us,

00:15:01.090 --> 00:15:04.270 align:middle line:84%
gave me a different
kind of seeing.

00:15:04.270 --> 00:15:07.180 align:middle line:84%
It was one of the most
profound periods of my life.

00:15:07.180 --> 00:15:12.460 align:middle line:90%


00:15:12.460 --> 00:15:15.180 align:middle line:84%
And it was really
being young and free--

00:15:15.180 --> 00:15:16.470 align:middle line:90%
I was not in a relationship.

00:15:16.470 --> 00:15:18.000 align:middle line:90%
I had no children yet.

00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:20.190 align:middle line:84%
I could just be by
myself with the elements.

00:15:20.190 --> 00:15:23.220 align:middle line:84%
And as I sat up on top of
the mountain in the morning,

00:15:23.220 --> 00:15:28.770 align:middle line:84%
and I watched the air go by,
and sat by my fire each night,

00:15:28.770 --> 00:15:31.950 align:middle line:84%
which was my light and my
company, sat by my fire

00:15:31.950 --> 00:15:34.470 align:middle line:84%
and played my guitar
