00:15:34.470 --> 00:15:36.120 align:middle line:84%
as I worked with
the rain catchers

00:15:36.120 --> 00:15:39.030 align:middle line:84%
that I built, or had to just
conserve every drop of water,

00:15:39.030 --> 00:15:41.400 align:middle line:84%
