but a surface pattern,

00:15:55.350 --> 00:15:57.900 align:middle line:84%
but if you looked
very deep into it,

00:15:57.900 --> 00:16:01.630 align:middle line:84%
then you got to see another
pattern that would take shape.

00:16:01.630 --> 00:16:04.200 align:middle line:84%
Well, it's the same way
once we remove ourselves

00:16:04.200 --> 00:16:07.680 align:middle line:84%
from all the things we think
we need in this culture.

00:16:07.680 --> 00:16:09.900 align:middle line:90%
We begin to see differently.

00:16:09.900 --> 00:16:13.470 align:middle line:84%
