emerges that is normally

00:16:13.470 --> 00:16:16.380 align:middle line:84%
obliterated by all
the sensation that's

00:16:16.380 --> 00:16:20.210 align:middle line:84%
coming at us from signs and
noise and movies and radio,

00:16:20.210 --> 00:16:23.010 align:middle line:84%
that when you remove
that for long enough,

00:16:23.010 --> 00:16:25.650 align:middle line:90%
it's like your screen clears.

00:16:25.650 --> 00:16:28.470 align:middle line:84%
And it really was,
for me, a kind

00:16:28.470 --> 00:16:33.580 align:middle line:84%
of revelation of the
perfect sanctity of nature.

00:16:33.580 --> 00:16:35.460 align:middle line:84%
And what got me down
