00:16:35.460 --> 00:16:39.300 align:middle line:84%
is that as I sat up there, and
I watched civilization coming up

00:16:39.300 --> 00:16:41.070 align:middle line:84%
the highways that I
could see from there

00:16:41.070 --> 00:16:42.780 align:middle line:84%
