00:16:49.620 --> 00:16:51.700 align:middle line:90%
taken by very many people.

00:16:51.700 --> 00:16:54.750 align:middle line:84%
And I knew that I had to
come down off the mountain

00:16:54.750 --> 00:17:00.420 align:middle line:84%
and help stop that nonsensical
expansion of culture

00:17:00.420 --> 00:17:03.270 align:middle line:84%
into nature before we
lose it all, because we

00:17:03.270 --> 00:17:04.560 align:middle line:90%
lose our perspective.

00:17:04.560 --> 00:17:07.410 align:middle line:84%
And that's a very
important perspective--

00:17:07.410 --> 00:17:09.540 align:middle line:90%
not just that nature has a plan.

00:17:09.540 --> 00:17:11.720 align:middle line:90%
Nature is the plan.

00:17:11.720 --> 00:17:14.700 align:middle line:84%
And we need to remove
ourselves from culture every so

00:17:14.700 --> 00:17:17.280 align:middle line:84%
often in order to
listen to the music,

00:17:17.280 --> 00:17:21.060 align:middle line:84%
in order to really
understand the language.

