00:18:35.730 --> 00:18:40.680 align:middle line:84%
the strength of my back, my
mind to think, my eyes to see.

00:18:40.680 --> 00:18:44.160 align:middle line:84%
Only what I had with me and what
I could communicate with around

00:18:44.160 --> 00:18:46.470 align:middle line:90%
me had value.

00:18:46.470 --> 00:18:49.560 align:middle line:84%
And that reset my
values, and that mountain

00:18:49.560 --> 00:18:52.980 align:middle line:84%
will always be sacred
to me, as will nature.

00:18:52.980 --> 00:18:54.523 align:middle line:90%
And that's my soul story.

