00:21:39.400 --> 00:21:41.590 align:middle line:84%
let her know that it was
time for me to move on.

00:21:41.590 --> 00:21:44.890 align:middle line:84%
The truth of the
matter is the fear

00:21:44.890 --> 00:21:49.780 align:middle line:84%
of not leaving became greater
than the fear of leaving.

00:21:49.780 --> 00:21:53.360 align:middle line:84%
And once-- it was almost like
an out-of-body experience.

00:21:53.360 --> 00:21:57.820 align:middle line:84%
It was like my soul had said,
in many ways, through my body

00:21:57.820 --> 00:21:59.110 align:middle line:90%
and through my--

00:21:59.110 --> 00:22:03.280 align:middle line:84%
just in my everyday thoughts
was communicating with me

00:22:03.280 --> 00:22:08.110 align:middle line:84%
that there was more for me to
do and that I needed to move on.

00:22:08.110 --> 00:22:14.060 align:middle line:84%
Right now, one of my goals
is to really find my truth,

00:22:14.060 --> 00:22:16.660 align:middle line:84%
because I feel like the inner
journey is the most fascinating

00:22:16.660 --> 00:22:18.430 align:middle line:90%
journey that you can take.

00:22:18.430 --> 00:22:21.010 align:middle line:84%
And there's a lot to
learn about oneself.

00:22:21.010 --> 00:22:24.230 align:middle line:84%
There are just so many ways
I can grow, and I know that.

00:22:24.230 --> 00:22:27.160 align:middle line:84%
And the key is to figure
out what those are,

00:22:27.160 --> 00:22:30.670 align:middle line:84%
and then to be conscious so
that you can, every day, try

00:22:30.670 --> 00:22:34.660 align:middle line:84%
to implement those ways that's
going to take you where you

00:22:34.660 --> 00:22:37.210 align:middle line:84%
want to go, into
that peaceful realm

00:22:37.210 --> 00:22:39.040 align:middle line:90%
that we all want to be in.

00:22:39.040 --> 00:22:41.050 align:middle line:90%
And it's not an overnight thing.

00:22:41.050 --> 00:22:42.400 align:middle line:90%
I was at the company for--

00:22:42.400 --> 00:22:44.440 align:middle line:84%
I was really sort of
unhappy for five years.

00:22:44.440 --> 00:22:47.980 align:middle line:84%
If anyone understands that
paralyzing handcuffs of fear,

00:22:47.980 --> 00:22:49.820 align:middle line:90%
I do, because I experienced it.

00:22:49.820 --> 00:22:53.560 align:middle line:84%
But I also know there's
another life beyond that fear.

00:22:53.560 --> 00:22:58.600 align:middle line:84%
And it just takes that
finally finding that courage

00:22:58.600 --> 00:23:02.510 align:middle line:84%
to take those steps,
and anybody can do it.

00:23:02.510 --> 00:23:04.120 align:middle line:90%
Anybody can do it.

